		<title>Who Does the Autopsy?</title>
		<link>https://www.jeffersonswheel.org/2015/who-does-the-autopsy</link>
		<comments>https://www.jeffersonswheel.org/2015/who-does-the-autopsy#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Wed, 25 Mar 2015 06:49:40 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator>David Evans</dc:creator>
