		<title>Scientists work to keep hackers out of implanted medical devices</title>
		<link>https://www.jeffersonswheel.org/2010/scientists-work-to-keep-hackers-out-of-implanted-medical-devices</link>
		<comments>https://www.jeffersonswheel.org/2010/scientists-work-to-keep-hackers-out-of-implanted-medical-devices#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Mon, 19 Apr 2010 22:58:05 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator>David Evans</dc:creator>
